  "name": "Improved Dirge of Doom",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/water_03.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>The foreboding tone of your dirge is especially effective at unsettling your enemies.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Ability to perform dirge of doom.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>The range of your dirge of doom ability is extended to 60 feet. Additionally, if a creature is shaken from another effect, the effect of your dirge of doom is changed to frightened for that specific creature. This benefit cannot cause a creature to become panicked, even if a target is already frightened from another effect.<br/><br/><b>Normal</b><br/>The range of dirge of doom is 30 feet. A creature that is already shaken cannot become frightened by dirge of doom. Once affected by this feat, a creature cannot be affected by it again for 24 hours.",
